Product Manager
Greenstar Social Marketing Pakistan (Guarantee) Limited
Posted :29 April, 2014
1,078 views
Experience: 5 to 7 yearsJob Location: KarachiCountry: PakistanPositions: 1Job Type: Full Time
Department / Job Category: Sales and Marketing
Last Date: 05 May, 2014
Salary: -
Job Summary:
The position reports to Head of Health Services Marketing and is responsible for all aspect of product management including development and execution of marketing strategies, launching of new products, campaign planning, development and printing of promotional material and participation in the training of field force.
Key Accountabilities:
• Responsible for the overall management of the assigned products.• Plan and develop marketing strategies for the existing and new products.• Develop quarterly/annually promotional plans and ensure implementation• Impart knowledge and training of and updates about products to the sales/field force.• Develop plans for launching new products / identify new business opportunities for the assigned products.• Design and develop the product literature and promotional material• Conduct field visits periodically and facilitate the field staff (MIOs)• Monitor sales analysis and sales targets• Maintain strong coordination with the zonal managers for the execution of the product strategies• Participate in conferences and seminars• Conceptualize and materialize brand reminders/giveaways for Health Care Providers.• Prepare annual budget for the products.• Develop and maintain relationships with KOLs (Key Opinion Leaders)
Qualification, Experience & Competencies
• MBBS Doctor (male/female) preferably with MBA Marketing.• Hands on experience of 2 to 3 years as Product Manager in a leading pharmaceutical company would be preferred.• Strong aptitude for product promotion.• Excellent communication skills.
